## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential biases inherent in historical documents. Many justifications for slavery were context-specific and may not be fully captured in the available literature. Additionally, the interpretations of religious and philosophical texts can vary, leading to different conclusions about their role in justifying slavery. Further research could explore these nuances in greater detail.

